Arrangement.text:
CHORUS: [E]You are the [E/G#]Lord, the f[A2]amous One, famous One [C#m7]Great is Your [B]name in all the [A]earth The [E]heavens decl[E/G#]are You’re gl[A2]orious, glorious [C#m7]Great is Your f[B]ame beyond the [E]earth [E/G# D2 A2]
VERSE 1: And for [F#m7]all You’ve done and [E/G#]yet to do With [A]ev’ry breath, I’m pr[E]aising You Des[F#m7]ire of nations and [E/G#]ev’ry heart You al[A]one are God, You al[Bsus]one are God
VERSE 2: The M[F#m7]orning Star is sh[E/G#]ining through And [A]ev’ry eye is w[E]atching You Re[F#m7]vealed by nature and m[E/G#]iracles You are b[A]eautiful, You are b[Bsus]eautiful
